\overline{\rho\theta} & = & \sum_{i}\eta_{i}\theta_{i}=\sum_{i}\sigma_{i}\rho_{i}\theta_{i}=\sum_{i}\sigma_{i}\frac{p_{r}}{R\theta_{i}}\pi^{\frac{\kappa}{1-\kappa}}\theta_{i}=\frac{p_{r}}{R}\pi^{\frac{\kappa}{1-\kappa}}
