) can be split up into
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{\partial\eta_{i}}{\partial t}+\mathbf{u}_{i}\cdot\nabla\eta_{i}+\eta_{i}\nabla\cdot\mathbf{u}_{i}=\sum_{j\ne i}\left(\eta_{j}S_{ji}-\eta_{i}S_{ij}\right).\label{eq:etaTransport-split}
